title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Benefactor Take Over
content:
Celebrate the Benefactor brand’s extensive catalog of premium vehicles this week with discounts and bonuses on everything from sleek sports cars to armored sedans.

The artistry of this majestic German auto manufacturer is on full display — experience a wide range of Benefactor models for yourself in the Premium Deluxe Motorsport showroom and at the Test Track inside the LS Car Meet.
